{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":12606,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":2314,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"数理基科为通常的基科*1，*2，为物理系下属班级。物理系有两套培养方案：物理专业和基科专业，大二下自由分流。\n基科培养方案的特点是留出15（或者20？）学分选修外系核心课，并且要求学生大三大四做seminar，即在全校内找导师做本科生科研。概括来说，就是方便转行。\n随着强基计划与各个书院的落实，基科方案可能会变动，不知道未来如何。\n\n基科*3，*4是化生基科，不懂。","timestamp":1592806467,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12645,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":2314,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"历史上的基科发生过多次编制变动，在此不再详述","timestamp":1592806703,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12669,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":2314,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"搞♂基科学班，以及#696","timestamp":1592806827,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12676,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":2314,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 谢谢！","timestamp":1592806873,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12979,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":2314,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"基科分为数理基科（基科x1、基科x2，归物理系）和化生基科（基科x3，归化学系）","timestamp":1592808862,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":2314,"reply":5,"tag":null,"text":"求科普，基科是什么呢？是一个单独的专业还是一类专业的合称还是单独编班啥的呀？","timestamp":1592806248,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782582,"url":"","vote":{}}}